Mr Cummings has claimed that the reason that Mr Johnson is backing Liz Truss in the Tory leadership race is that she is as "mad as a box of snakes" and if she "blows" there will be another leadership contest in which he can make a return. In his latest blog, Mr Cummings said that he gave the nickname "human handgrenade" because she "compulsively" leaked things to the press. He said: "Boris is supporting Truss, Why? 1) He thinks its the best way to stop Sunak. 2) He knows Truss is mad as a box of snakes and is thinking "there's a chance she blows, there's another contest and I can return". FOLLOW BELOW FOR LIVE UPDATES... 